        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Voluntary Protection Program Act</b></p> <p>This bill provides statutory authority for the voluntary protection program within the Occupational Safety and Health Administration. Under the program, workplaces that implement comprehensive safety and health management systems are exempt from certain paperwork and inspection requirements.</p>]]>
        </text>
